Interface Command

All Known Subinterfaces:
OrderCommand
All Known Implementing Classes:
AdvanceOrderCommand, AirliftOrderCommand, AssignCountriesCommand, BlockadeOrderCommand, BombOrderCommand, DeployOrderCommand, EditContinentCommand, EditCountryCommand, EditMapCommand, EditNeighborCommand, GamePlayerCommand, InvalidCommand, LoadGameCommand, LoadMapCommand, NegotiateOrderCommand, PassCommand, SaveGameCommand, SaveMapCommand, ShowCardsCommand, ShowMapCommand, TournamentCommand, ValidateMapCommand
public interface Command
Interface implemented by all executable commands.

A Command object represents an executable command produced by parsing a string command provided by user.
